flowchart TD
  U[User message] --> PS[Prompt Builder]
  subgraph PS[Prompt Builder]
    SP[Stable Prefix
(System + tool schemas + rules)]
    VS[Volatile Suffix
(user msg + retrieved ctx + tool outputs)]
  end
  PS -->|SP byte-identical across turns| L[Local LLM Server
(prefix match + KV cache reuse)]
  PS -->|VS changes per turn| L
  L --> A[Assistant output]
  L --> TC[Tool call JSON]
  TC --> T[Tools/Services]
  T --> TO[Tool outputs]
  TO --> VS
  M[Telemetry/Git status] -->|logged externally (not in SP)| OBS[Observability]
